## ğŸš— Engineering Insight
Rear stagger tuning is critical for oval performance. This project:
- Demonstrates how small changes in tire circumference affect corner entry, rotation, and straight-line stability  
- Builds a data-driven method for choosing qualifying setup  
- Includes a recommendation email to the crew chief
